{"tid":1103540,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"高通下一代處理器 Snapdragon 865 曝光，或集成 5G 晶片+ LPDDR 5","createTime":"2019-04-12T13:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T16:18:45.000Z","uid":50534,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"72ed809fd3225d31945f8b917030a68c28847319","tid":1103540,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/04/12/snapdragon-865-build-in-5g-modem/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F04%2F12%2Fsnapdragon-865-build-in-5g-modem%2F&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8JmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=0ee2c93b\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/04/12/snapdragon-865-build-in-5g-modem/</a><br />\n隨著各大手機廠商的旗艦機型陸續推出，Qualcomm 的年度旗艦處理器 Snapdragon 855 也被大家熟知。Snapdragon 855 作為目前 Android 平台綜合性能最強的處理器可謂無懈可擊，但卻沒有內置支援 5G 頻段的基帶。而 Qualcomm 的下一代旗艦處理器將完善該缺陷，就是即將來到的 Snapdragon 865。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據知名爆料人士 Roland Quandt 透露，內部型號為 SM8250 的 Qualcomm 下一代旗艦平台將支援 LPDDR5 記憶體，雖然 Qualcomm 暫未公佈 SM8250 的最終命名，但是按照以往命名規則，SM8250 應該會被命名為 Snapdragon 865。爆料消息顯示，Qualcomm 已經擁有搭載 LPDDR5 記憶體 + Snapdragon 865 旗艦平台的樣機，目前正在進行測試。且 Qualcomm 還有一款尚未發布的 5G Modem SDM55，其代號為「Huracan」，可能是 Snapdragon 865 集成 SDM55 5G Modem，能實現對 5G 網絡的支援。<br />\n<br />\n按照以往的慣例，Qualcomm Snapdragon 865 旗艦處理器會在今年年底發布，各大手機廠商於明年年初推出相應的手機設備。而它的對手將是來自中國的華為新一代麒麟 985 旗艦處理器和 Apple 的 A13 仿生處理器。"},{"pid":"08b894b4b96556fa821fe855ad014ebc8da22f8a","tid":1103540,"uid":158977,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"隔離公司一定好葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea915027df4275969edb5898d1b5662ac9ec3d2","tid":1103540,"uid":240918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08b894b4b96556fa821fe855ad014ebc8da22f8a","tid":1103540,"uid":158977,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"隔離公司一定好葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1